{'hash': 'e1634c509070b949201289e84296927df6af38ab', 'query': "SELECT T1.Device, AVG(T3.Quantity) FROM device AS T1 JOIN stock AS T3 ON T1.Device_ID = T3.Device_ID WHERE T3.Shop_ID = (SELECT Shop_ID FROM shop WHERE Shop_Name = 'XYZ') AND T3.Quantity > 100 ORDER BY T3.Quantity DESC", 'template': 'SELECT #COLUMN#, AVG(#COLUMN#) FROM #TABLE# JOIN #TABLE# ON #COLUMN# = #COLUMN# WHERE #COLUMN# = (SELECT #COLUMN# FROM #TABLE# WHERE #COLUMN# = #VALUE#) AND #COLUMN# > #VALUE# ORDER BY #COLUMN# DESC'}
